{"tid":145304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強國賤男女踩碎天鵝蛋 仲毒打天鵝爸媽","createTime":"2017-03-06T07:01:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-07T09:45:32.000Z","uid":10338,"like":4,"dislike":180,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4486a2ef73424eb690dbe216420d7b4f7b664ad8","tid":145304,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T07:01:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/vqstf7xu\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fvqstf7xu&h=7e94a1f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/yaphben6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fyaphben6&h=0b53d461&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/71krmnd9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F71krmnd9&h=7bcb1952&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/x8a0rjfy\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fx8a0rjfy&h=d72b35d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n內地再現缺德遊客。有江蘇揚州網友爆料，周六於當地著名景點瘦西湖，一名戴著口罩，年約20歲左右的男子突然越過護欄，走入湖邊，繼而將地上的天鵝蛋踩碎。當時有黑天鵝奮力護蛋，變態男竟然出手襲擊，將天鵝翅膀打至流血。<br />\n<br />\n網民指，兩隻黑天鵝眼看鵝蛋慘被踩碎，久久不肯離去，其中一隻天鵝更對天哀嚎，情景讓人心碎。"},{"pid":"019c254e36ae97b3a521f72a98907156410b8e28","tid":145304,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T07:04:08.000Z","msg":"個個淨係影相"},{"pid":"45a8242b513427b25aaa75081b09bfc781f9d4c8","tid":145304,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T07:04:41.000Z","msg":"個個掛住拍，無人救天鵝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17b2ea66f23f77a81c104bfaf3597cefac366c2b","tid":145304,"uid":48875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T07:06:37.000Z","msg":"嘩屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fa2ba382db32a6fcfb49782ba346fab9dee2958","tid":145304,"uid":71967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T07:07:05.000Z","msg":"屌 ON9"},{"pid":"b